@startuml cfdp-profile-conformance
' Requirements: L1-FDP-001, L2-FDP-004
' Source: docs/specs/ccsds-file-delivery-protocol/L1.md, docs/specs/ccsds-file-delivery-protocol/L2.md
title Baseline CFDP Profile Declaration and Conformance Inspection
autonumber

actor "CI Pipeline" as CI
participant "Conformance Test Suite" as CTS
participant "Profile Declaration\n(docs/specs, TBD-008)" as DECL
participant "CFDP Engine" as ENG

== Profile load ==
CI -> CTS ++ : run cfdp-conformance job
CTS -> DECL ++ : read declared baseline profile\n(transmission mode, checksum type,\nsegment size, fault handlers, timers)
DECL --> CTS -- : single declared profile (CCSDS 727.0-B subset)

== Per-test-case inspection ==
loop for each baseline conformance test case
    CTS -> CTS : verify test case references\nthe declared CFDP profile
    alt test case references declared profile
        CTS -> ENG ++ : execute test case against engine\nconfigured with declared profile
        ENG --> CTS -- : observed PDU behaviour
        CTS -> CTS : assert behaviour matches profile
    else test case missing or divergent profile reference
        CTS --> CI : FAIL: test case does not reference\nthe single declared CFDP profile
        note right of CI
            L2-FDP-004 AC: GIVEN baseline conformance
            tests WHEN the profile declaration is
            reviewed THEN each test case references
            a single declared CFDP profile.
        end note
    end
end

== Verdict ==
CTS --> CI -- : conformance report\n(profile id, pass/fail per case)
CI -> CI : gate merge on conformance result
@enduml
